%N A395881 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {6,7} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395881 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395881 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Wiki page indexing sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395881 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo} = A221184.
%t A395881 (* Cf. A394862 with p=6 and q=7. *)
